"""Test get_ficon_emulation_thread_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_ficon_emulation_thread_stats(ficon_emulation_thread_id
    =self.p_data.ficon_emu_thread_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.
    time_now, end_time=self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.FICON_EMU_THR))
